text: Ajit Singh Pal is an Indian politician and Minister of State in the Government of Uttar Pradesh. He was member of the Uttar Pradesh Legislative Assembly from Sikandra assembly constituency of Kanpur Dehat district. ==References== ==External links== *UP: BJP retains Sikandara assembly seat in Kanpur (Times of India) Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Indian politicians
